    "Fix: snMap built once per render by sorting all transactions by _addedAt timestamp ascending. SN 1 = oldest entry, highest SN = latest entry added. Duplicates get _addedAt:new Date().toISOString() in the reducer (already in place), so they always land at the top of the SN sequence.",
