    "UnifiedLedger desktop: globalIdx reads unifiedSnMap[accId__txId] — SN is per-account within the unified view, using the same _addedAt logic.",
    "Fallback: transactions without _addedAt (imported or very old) fall back to uid string comparison, preserving relative order.",
