    "Balance adjustment is computed atomically: credits removed reduce the balance, debits removed increase it — matching the single-delete behaviour. Cards use outstanding instead of balance.",
    "Three new reducer cases: MASS_DEL_BANK_TX (adjusts bank balance), MASS_DEL_CARD_TX (adjusts card outstanding), MASS_DEL_CASH_TX (adjusts cash balance) — each accepts a Set of transaction IDs.",
