    "Child Education Plan Calculator: inputs — education cost today, child's current age, target education age, education inflation (default 10%), expected investment return, current savings, annual SIP step-up, planned SIP comparison; outputs — required flat SIP, step-up SIP starting amount, future education cost, total invested, growth, shortfall vs planned SIP; corpus build-up bar chart vs target; current savings FV benefit callout",
